📋 BASE URL
text
http://localhost:5000
🔐 STEP 1: Authentication (সবার আগে)
1.1 Register Admin
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Body:

json
{
  "name": "Super Admin",
  "email": "admin@fastfeast.com",
  "password": "admin123456",
  "phone": "+8801712345678",
  "role": "admin"
}
Response: Token পাবেন

1.2 Login Admin
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Body:

json
{
  "email": "admin@fastfeast.com",
  "password": "admin123456"
}
Response থেকে Token কপি করুন:

json
{
  "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..."
}
এই Token সব Admin API তে ব্যবহার করবেন

👑 STEP 2: Admin APIs (Admin Token দিয়ে)
2.1 Get All Users
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users?page=1&limit=10
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Response:

json
{
  "success": true,
  "count": 1,
  "users": [...]
}
2.2 Get Single User (ID দিয়ে)
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/USER_ID
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Note: USER_ID = উপরের Response থেকে _id নিন

2.3 Update User Status
text
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/USER_ID/status
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "status": "active"
}
2.4 Update User Role
text
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/USER_ID/role
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "role": "admin"
}
2.5 Delete User
text
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/USER_ID
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
🏪 STEP 3: Restaurant APIs
3.1 Register Restaurant Owner
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Body:

json
{
  "name": "Pizza Palace Owner",
  "email": "owner@pizzapalace.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "+8801712345678",
  "role": "restaurant"
}
3.2 Login Restaurant Owner
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Body:

json
{
  "email": "owner@pizzapalace.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
Token নিন: RESTAURANT_TOKEN

3.3 Create Restaurant (Restaurant Token দিয়ে)
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/restaurants
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer RESTAURANT_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "restaurantName": "Pizza Palace",
  "description": "Best authentic Italian pizza in town.",
  "cuisineType": ["Italian", "Pizza", "Pasta"],
  "address": {
    "street": "House 23, Road 7, Gulshan-1",
    "city": "Dhaka",
    "state": "Dhaka",
    "zipCode": "1212",
    "country": "Bangladesh"
  },
  "phone": "+8801712345678",
  "email": "info@pizzapalace.com",
  "deliveryTime": 30,
  "deliveryCharge": 50,
  "minimumOrder": 200
}
Response থেকে _id নিন: RESTAURANT_ID

3.4 Get All Restaurants (Public)
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/restaurants?page=1&limit=10
No Auth Needed

3.5 Get Single Restaurant
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID
👑 STEP 4: Admin Restaurant APIs (Admin Token দিয়ে)
4.1 Get All Restaurants (Admin View)
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/restaurants?page=1&limit=10
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN
4.2 Get Single Restaurant (Admin)
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN
4.3 Verify Restaurant
text
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID/verify
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN
4.4 Update Restaurant Status
text
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID/status
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "status": "active"
}
4.5 Delete Restaurant (Admin)
text
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN
📋 STEP 5: Menu APIs
5.1 Create Menu Item (Restaurant Token দিয়ে)
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/menu
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer RESTAURANT_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "restaurant": "RESTAURANT_ID",
  "name": "Margherita Pizza",
  "description": "Classic pizza with tomato and mozzarella",
  "price": 450,
  "category": "mains",
  "isVegetarian": true,
  "isSpicy": false,
  "preparationTime": 15
}
Response থেকে _id নিন: MENU_ID

5.2 Get All Menu Items
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menu?restaurantId=RESTAURANT_ID&page=1&limit=20
5.3 Get Single Menu Item
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menu/MENU_ID
5.4 Update Menu Item
text
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/menu/MENU_ID
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer RESTAURANT_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "price": 480
}
5.5 Delete Menu Item
text
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/menu/MENU_ID
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer RESTAURANT_TOKEN
📦 STEP 6: Order APIs
6.1 Register Customer
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Body:

json
{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "customer@test.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "+8801712345678",
  "role": "customer"
}
6.2 Login Customer
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Body:

json
{
  "email": "customer@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
Token নিন: CUSTOMER_TOKEN

6.3 Create Order (Customer Token দিয়ে)
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/orders
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer CUSTOMER_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "restaurant": "RESTAURANT_ID",
  "items": [
    {
      "menuItem": "MENU_ID",
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 450
    }
  ],
  "deliveryAddress": {
    "street": "House 12, Road 5",
    "city": "Dhaka",
    "state": "Dhaka",
    "zipCode": "1212",
    "country": "Bangladesh"
  },
  "paymentMethod": "cod"
}
Response থেকে _id নিন: ORDER_ID

6.4 Get Orders (Customer)
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders?page=1&limit=10
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer CUSTOMER_TOKEN
6.5 Get Single Order
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders/ORDER_ID
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer CUSTOMER_TOKEN
6.6 Update Order Status (Restaurant)
text
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/orders/ORDER_ID/status
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer RESTAURANT_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "orderStatus": "confirmed"
}
💳 STEP 7: Payment APIs
7.1 Create Payment Intent
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/payments/create-payment-intent
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer CUSTOMER_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "orderId": "ORDER_ID"
}
7.2 Get Payment Status
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/payments/status/ORDER_ID
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer CUSTOMER_TOKEN
📝 STEP 8: Blog APIs
8.1 Create Blog (Admin Token দিয়ে)
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/admin/blogs
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "title": "My First Blog Post",
  "content": "This is the full blog content...",
  "category": "food",
  "tags": ["food", "recipes"],
  "status": "published"
}
Response থেকে _id নিন: BLOG_ID

8.2 Get All Blogs (Public)
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/blog?page=1&limit=10
8.3 Get Blog by Slug
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/blog/slug/my-first-blog-post
8.4 Update Blog (Admin)
text
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/blogs/BLOG_ID
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "title": "Updated Blog Title"
}
8.5 Delete Blog (Admin)
text
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/admin/blogs/BLOG_ID
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN
⭐ STEP 9: Review APIs
9.1 Create Review (Customer Token দিয়ে)
text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/reviews
Headers:

text
Authorization: Bearer CUSTOMER_TOKEN
Body:

json
{
  "restaurant": "RESTAURANT_ID",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excellent food and service!",
  "reviewType": "restaurant"
}
9.2 Get All Reviews
text
GET http://localhost:5000/api/reviews?restaurantId=RESTAURANT_ID&page=1&limit=10
